---
title: Paprika Chicken in a Lemony Sauce with Pistachio Rice & Roasted Carrots
description: Lemon is our go-to ingredient for brightening up any meal, and this dish is positively bursting with citrusy goodness! Paprika-coated chicken is drizzled with a creamy, lemon-and-thyme-spiked pan sauce that’d taste good on pretty much anything. On the side, there’s tender roasted carrots and steamy rice with lemon zest and pistachios. When life gives you lemons, you know what to do.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6076d4a9912d7429ec352547-7f742805.jpg
